## 🔍 Decision Tree

```
Implementing file delete functionality?
├─ Define file item interface
│  └─ fileId type: string | number (NOT just number)
├─ Create delete API function
│  └─ Accept fileId: string | number parameter
├─ Implement delete confirmation
│  ├─ Add state: showDeleteConfirmDialog, fileToDelete
│  ├─ Add handler: handleDeleteFileClick
│  └─ Export all state and setters (CRITICAL)
├─ Implement actual delete function
│  ├─ Convert fileId/seq to string for comparison
│  ├─ Call delete API
│  ├─ Update file list with String() conversion
│  └─ Show success/failure message
└─ Implement UI
   ├─ Delete button calls handleDeleteFileClick
   ├─ ConfirmDialog for confirmation
   └─ ConfirmDialog for success/failure message
```

